	<tr>
		
			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				A monks weapons are his hands. Except that all monk weapons, and most existing previous weapons are better than fists, at low level. Level 1 monk hands are 4 damage, 36 delay. Thats worse than rusties. Fighting batons (should be able to afford them by level 30) are equal to level 45 monk fists. Its a little help. Use em, if its better.<BR>
<BR>
A monks armor is his agility, unless of course, you have no AC items. AC is your armor. Agility adds very little AC. If you have lower than 75 agility, you lose your monk AC bonus, but otherwise its just another stat. AC is where its at.<BR>
<BR>
A monk should never carry more than 14 pounds, unless of course your higher level, and cant tank anyway. If you need to, loot those items. If your over 14 pounds, you lose Defense. Defense only. You still are offensively capable, and then you can just Feign Death if something gets on you. If your over level 35, feign death a few times on the ground, while other people build up taunt. <BR>
<BR>
A monk should learn fishing.. hehe.. anyone ever tried fishing? Wow. Go find a mage =P<BR>
<BR>
A monk should learn to be a tailor.. except of course for our really low intelligence, and that most people can buy cured silk by level 10. We dont learn the skill fast, and I'd just let it to other casters who need the raw silk anyway.<BR>
<BR>
Bind wound rocks =) =) =).. just some advice, after 200 skill, you can bind wound up to 70%<BR>
<BR>
A monk should not beg... thats just personal preference. I always traded spider silk and GLS if I didnt have any cash. I still dont have cash... so I occasionally get another GLS every now and then =P<BR>
<BR>
A monk shouldnt solo... although you can almost all your life. (Instill Doubt works wonders, once you start to lose your soloing ability) But you only kill about 1 creature ever 6-12 min. (mend wound times)<BR>
<BR>
A monk should be kind and generous, especially to me. =P<BR>
<BR>
<BR>
<BR>
I like the idealism, but EQ is just a game....<BR>
<BR>
Onigami Satsugai<BR>
Monk of the Ashen Order
